<plot>For over 20 years, Javier Gonzalez (Pedro Navarro) stood smiling pleasantly beneath the sizzling New Mexican sun and sold the daily newspaper to the passengers of passing cars. A modest man, Javier enjoyed the simple pleasures of life. "Writing on the Wall" both reveals these simple pleasures and ruminates on the significance they, as well as the man enjoying them, have in a modern world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?661601</url></doc>
